let amod = adobeopt.module("analytics");
let pmc = amod;
let pcl = amod;

// ---------------------------------------------
// PCL -- COMMON LIBRARY
adobeopt.extend( pcl, {

  beacon: {},
  
  firedBeacons: [],
  diagnostic: [ ],
  
  // pcl.initalize
  initalize: function( oEvt ) { 
    pcl.oEvt = oEvt;
    pcl.currentURL = window.location.href;
    pcl.scriptName = pcl.scriptNameFromURL();
  },
  
  // pcl.addEvent
  addEvent: function ( num, eVars, eProps ) { // ( event number, [evar list object] )
    var evStr = "";
    if ( typeof(num) === "string" ) { // supplied a string (for purchase, etc)
      evStr = num;
    } else { // number
      evStr = "event" + num;
    }
    if ( evStr == "event1" ) {
      pcl.beacon.isPageView = true;
    }
  /** IFDEF X_LAUNCH **/
    // eventnum = evStr.replace("event","");
    // if ( pmc.eventMap.hasOwnProperty( eventnum ) ) {
    // 	var e = pmc.eventMap[eventnum];
    // 	_satellite.setVar( e.n, "true" );
    // 	pmc.trackParams[ e.n ] = "true";
    // 	if ( e.rule ) {
    // 		pmc.trackParams[ "track" ] = e.n;
    // 		return; // don't add to sobject
    // 	}
    // }
  /** ENDIF **/
  
    if ( typeof eVars === "number" || typeof eVars === "string" ) { // override, allows event value
      evStr += "=" + eVars.toString();
      eVars = undefined;
    }
  
    if ( pcl.isUndef(pcl.beacon.events) )  {
      pcl.beacon.events = evStr;
      // pcl.beacon.linkTrackEvents = evStr;
    } else {
      pcl.beacon.events += "," + evStr;
      // pcl.beacon.linkTrackEvents += "," + evStr;
    }
    
    pcl.processEProps( eProps );
    pcl.addEvars( eVars );
  },
  // pcl.processEProps
  processEProps: function( eProps ) { // add attributes from eProp block, only pageName for now
    var eventID = 0;
    if ( ! (pcl.isObj( eProps ) && pcl.isStr( eProps.pageName ) ) )
      return;
    pcl.oEvt.pageName = val;
    pcl.oEvt.siteSection = val.substring( 0, val.indexOf( "|" ) - 1 );
  },
  // pcl.addEvars
  addEvars: function ( evars ) { 
    if ( pcl.isObj( evars ) )
      for(var key in evars)
        pcl.addEvar( key, evars[key] );
  },
  // pcl.addEvar
  addEvar: function (id, sValue) {
    if ( pcl.isNum(id) )
      id = "eVar" + id;
  /** IFDEF LAUNCH **/
    // evarnum = id.replace("eVar","");
    // if ( pmc.evarMap.hasOwnProperty( evarnum ) ) {
    // 	_satellite.setVar( pmc.evarMap[evarnum], sValue );
    // 	pmc.trackParams[ pmc.evarMap[evarnum] ] = sValue;
    // }
  /** ENDIF **/
    pcl.beacon[id] = sValue;
    // if ( pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars === 'None' )
    // 	pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars = id;
    // else
    // 	pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars += "," + id;
  
  },
  // pcl.addEvar
  addProp: function (id, sValue) {
    if ( pcl.isNum(id) )
      id = "prop" + id;
  /** IFDEF LAUNCH **/
    // evarnum = id.replace("prop","");
    // if ( pmc.propMap.hasOwnProperty( evarnum ) ) {
    // 	_satellite.setVar( pmc.propMap[evarnum], sValue );
    // 	pmc.trackParams[ pmc.propMap[evarnum] ] = sValue;
    // }
  /** ENDIF **/
    pcl.beacon[id] = sValue;
    // if ( pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars === 'None' )
    // 	pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars = id;
    // else
    // 	pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars += "," + id;
  
  },// pcl.setProductString
  setProductString: function( prodStr, fixUp ) {
    // if ( pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars === 'None' )
    // 	pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars = "products";
    // else
    // 	pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars += ",products";
    if ( fixUp == true ) {
      prodStr = pmc.fixUpProdString( prodStr );
    }
    pcl.beacon.products = prodStr;
  },
  setProducts: function( prodArray ) {
    // if ( pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars === 'None' )
    // 	pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars = "products";
    // else
    // 	pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars += ",products";
    pcl.beacon.products = prodStr;
  },
  addProduct: function( prodProps, evars ) {
    var prodString = pcl.strOrBlank( prodProps.category ); // REVIEW
    prodString += ";" + pcl.strOrBlank( prodProps.product );
    prodString += ";" + pcl.strOrBlank( prodProps.quantity );
    prodString += ";" + pcl.strOrBlank( prodProps.totalPrice );
    prodString += ";" + pcl.strOrBlank( prodProps.incrementor );
    prodString += ";" + pcl.strOrBlank( prodProps.merchandising );
    // REVIEW -- how about a debug function to look for unused properties to find typos?
    // REVIEW -- process evar block
    
    if ( !pcl.isStr( pcl.beacon.products ) )
      pcl.beacon.products = "";
    else if ( pcl.beacon.products !== "" )
      prodString = ";" + prodString;
    pcl.beacon.products += prodString;
  },
  // pcl.submitToAnalytics
  fireDeferred: function() {
    let deferred = sessionStorage.getItem("aopt-analytics-deferred");
    if ( typeof deferred == "string" ) {
      sessionStorage.removeItem("aopt-analytics-deferred");
      let deferedEvents = JSON.parse( deferred );
      deferedEvents.forEach( function( beacon ) {
        pcl.beacon = beacon;
        pcl.submitToAnalytics();
      });
      
    }
  },
  // pcl.submitToAnalytics
  submitToAnalytics: function() {
    // if ( pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars === "None" )
    // 	pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars = 'events';
    // else
    // 	pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars += ',events';
    var msg = "";
    // pcl.beacon.sa(pmcPlatform.getProp("account"));
  
    if ( pcl.beacon.defer === true ) {
      delete pcl.beacon.defer;
      sessionStorage.setItem("aopt-analytics-deferred", JSON.stringify( [ pcl.beacon ] )  );
      pcl.clearSObj();
      return;
    }
  
    if ( pcl.beacon.isPageView === true ) {
      pmc.fixUpReferrer( true );
      if ( _satellite.getVar("useAlloy") ) {
        alloy( "sendEvent", { data: { __adobe: {
          analytics: pcl.beacon
        }}});
      } else {
        msg = s.t( pcl.beacon );
      }
      pmc.pageLoadFired = true;
    } else {
      pmc.fixUpReferrer( false );

      if ( _satellite.getVar("useAlloy") ) {
        pcl.beacon.linkType = "o";
        pcl.beacon.linkName = arguments[2] || "";
        pcl.beacon.linkUrl = window.location.href;
        alloy( "sendEvent", { data: { __adobe: {
                  analytics: pcl.beacon
        }}});
      } else {
        msg = s.tl( arguments[0] || true, 'o', arguments[2] || "", pcl.beacon );
      }
    }
    pcl.firedBeacons.push( pcl.beacon );
    adobeopt.logBeacon( pcl.beacon, arguments.length === 2);
    pcl.clearSObj();
  },
  // pcl.clearSObj
  clearSObj: function() {
    pcl.beacon = {};
    // pcl.beacon.linkTrackEvents = "None";
    // pcl.beacon.linkTrackVars = "None";
    // pcl.beacon.events = "None";
    // pcl.beacon.products = "";
    // for ( var i = 0 ; i <= 99 ; i++ )
    // 	s["eVar"+i] = undefined;
  },
  strOrBlank: function( o ) {
    // if the argument is a string or int, return it, otherwise an empty string
    if ( ! (pcl.isStr(o) || pcl.isNum(o) ) )
      return "";
    return o;
  },
  strBlank: function( s ) { // non-string and "" will BOTH return true, number returns false
    if ( pcl.isNum(s) )
      return false; // a number will always equal a non-blank string
    if ( ! pcl.isStr(s) ) 
      return true;
    return s.length === 0;
  },
  strNotBlank: function( s ) { // non string and "" will BOTH return false, number returns true
    if ( pcl.isNum(s) )
      return true; // a number will always equal a non-blank string
    if ( ! pcl.isStr(s) )
      return false;
    return s.length !== 0;
  },
  // pcl.scriptNameFromURL
  scriptNameFromURL: function() {
    var t = window.location.pathname;
    return t.substring( t.lastIndexOf( '/' )+1 );
  },
  sStart: function(strin, str) { return strin.slice(0, str.length) == str; },
  sEnd: function(strin, str) {	return strin.slice(-str.length) == str; },
  sContains: function(strin, str) { return strin.indexOf( str ) > -1; },
  sRemove: function(strin, str) { return strin.replace(str,"")  },
  
  isUndef: function( o ) { return typeof(o) === "undefined"; },
  isBool: function( o ) { return typeof(o) === "boolean"; },
  isNum: function( o ) { return typeof(o) === "number"; },
  isStr: function( o ) { return typeof(o) === "string"; },
  isFunc: function( o ) { return typeof(o) === "function"; },
  isObj: function( o ) { return typeof(o) === "object"; }  
});

// ANALYTICS BEACON

// ================================================
// >>> PRODUCT STRING MANAGEMENT

let escapeProdStringVal = pmc.escapeProdStringVal = function( s ) {
  // replace all | ; ,  with _
  return (s.toString().substring(0, 30).replace(/[|;,]/g, "_"));
}
let pstrProdBldr = pmc.pstrProdBldr = function( props ) {
  this.args = [
      "", // 0 category
      "", // 1 pid
      "1", // 2 quantity
      "", // 3 price
      "", // events 4
      "" // evars 5
  ];
  this.events = [ ];
  this.evars = [ ];
}
pstrProdBldr.prototype.addEvent = function( number, value ) {
  this.events.push( "event" + number + ( value ? "=" + value : "" ) );
};
pstrProdBldr.prototype.addEvar = function( number, value ) {
  this.evars.push( "eVar" + number + "=" + escapeProdStringVal(value) );
};
pstrProdBldr.prototype.category = function( v ) { return v ? this.args[0] = v : this.args[0] };
pstrProdBldr.prototype.sku = function( v ) { this.addEvar( 55, v ) };
pstrProdBldr.prototype.quantity = function( v ) { return v ? this.args[2] = v : this.args[2] };
pstrProdBldr.prototype.price = function( v ) { return v ? this.args[3] = v : this.args[3] };
pstrProdBldr.prototype.pid = function( v ) { this.addEvar( 52, v ); v ? this.args[1] = v : this.args[1] };
pstrProdBldr.prototype.prodId = pstrProdBldr.prototype.pid;
pstrProdBldr.prototype.prodName = function( v ) {  }; // we no longer use v53, use v52 classification instead
pstrProdBldr.prototype.pstr = function() {
  // "Category;Product;Quantity;Price;eventN=X[|eventN2=X2];eVarN=merch_category[|eVarN2=merch_category2]"
  this.args[4] = this.events.join("|");
  this.args[5] = this.evars.join("|");
  return this.args.join(";")
};

function oneOf( v, strOrArray ) { // 
  return strOrArray.indexOf(v) > -1;
}

pmc.prodsFromDataLayerObj = function( data, products, varient ) {

  products = products || [];
  if ( Array.isArray( data.products ) ) {
      data.products.forEach( function( prod ) {
          pmc.prodsFromDataLayerObj( prod, products, varient );
      });
  } else if ( typeof data == "object" && typeof data.pid === "string" ) {
      // single product directly in data
      let prod = new pstrProdBldr();
      if ( typeof data.pid === "string" ) {
          prod.pid( data.pid );
      }
      if ( typeof data.sku === "string" ) {
          prod.sku( data.sku );
      }
      if ( oneOf( typeof data.price, [ "string", "number" ] ) ) {
          prod.price( data.price.toString() );
      }
      if ( oneOf( varient, [ "purchase", "addToCart" ] ) && oneOf( typeof data.quantity, [ "string", "number" ] ) ) {
          prod.quantity( data.quantity.toString() );
          if ( varient == "addToCart" ) {
              prod.addEvar( 28, data.quantity.toString() );
          }
      }
      if ( varient == "searchPageView" ) {
        if ( oneOf( typeof data.searchDisplayRank, [ "string", "number" ] ) ) {
          prod.addEvar( 59, data.searchDisplayRank.toString() );
        }
      }
      if ( varient == "searchClick" ) {
        if ( oneOf( typeof data.searchIndex, [ "string", "number" ] ) ) {
          prod.addEvar( 59, data.searchIndex.toString() );
        }
      }      
      products.push( prod );
  };
  return products;
}


pmc.prodStrFromProds = function( prods ) {
  return prods.map( function( prod ) {
      return prod.pstr();
  }).join(",");
}

pmc.prodStrFromDataLayerObj = function( data, varient ) {
  return pmc.prodStrFromProds( pmc.prodsFromDataLayerObj( data, [], varient ) );
}

// let beacon = adobeopt.beacon = adobeopt.module( "beacon", {
//   events: {},

pmc.inPrivateElement = false;
pmc.detectPrivateElement = function(event) {
    try {
        pmc.inPrivateElement = event.target.closest("[data-bi-private]") !== null;
        if ( pmc.inPrivateElement ) {
            amod.log( "inPrivateElement: entering" );
        }
    } catch ( e ) {
        amod.exception( e );
    }
}
pmc.releasePrivateElementDebounced = adobeopt.debounce( function(event) {
    if ( pmc.inPrivateElement ) {
        amod.log( "inPrivateElement: releasing" );
        pmc.inPrivateElement = false;
    }
}, 500 );
pmc.releasePrivateElement = function(event) {
    if ( pmc.inPrivateElement ) {
        pmc.releasePrivateElementDebounced();
    }
}

document.addEventListener("mousedown", pmc.detectPrivateElement, { capture: true, passive: true } );
document.addEventListener("mouseup", pmc.releasePrivateElement, { capture: true, passive: true } );
document.addEventListener("click", pmc.releasePrivateElement, { capture: true, passive: true } );

// DATA LAYER EVENT HANDLERS

pmc.setFusionMetrics = function() {
  let fusionQueryId = window?.digitalData?.fusionQueryId;
  if ( fusionQueryId !== undefined ) {
    pcl.addProp( 11, fusionQueryId );
  }

  let searchTerm = window?.digitalData?.searchTerm;
  let actualSearchTerm = window?.digitalData?.actualSearchTerm;
  if ( tag.hasValue( actualSearchTerm ) && actualSearchTerm !== searchTerm ) {
    pcl.addEvar( 95, actualSearchTerm ); // what they typed
    pcl.addEvar( 96, searchTerm ); // what it was corrected to
  }

  let xfec = window?.digitalData?.xFusionExitCode?.toString?.();

  switch (xfec) {
      case "1":
        pcl.addEvent( 80 ); 
        break;
      case "2":
        pcl.addEvent( 81 ); 
        break;
      case "3":
        pcl.addEvent( 82 ); 
        // Expected output: "Mangoes and papayas are $2.79 a pound."
        break;
      case "4":
        pcl.addEvent( 83 ); 
        break;
      case "5":
        pcl.addEvent( 84 ); 
        break;
      case "6": // no results
        pcl.addEvent( 11 ); 
        break;
      case "7":
        pcl.addEvent( 85 ); 
        break;
      }
}

pmc.searchFireDeferred = function() {
  // report defered search initiation only if from previous page
  try {
    let searchInitJson = sessionStorage.getItem( "aopt-searchinitiation" );
    if ( searchInitJson != null ) {
      sessionStorage.removeItem( "aopt-searchinitiation" ); // now or never
      let searchInit = JSON.parse( searchInitJson );
      if ( document.referrer !== searchInit.fromUrl ) {
          amod.log( "searchDeferred: data found but referrer mismatch" );
      } else {
        if ( searchInit.searchKeyword == "[not found]" ) {
          searchInit.searchKeyword = window?.digitalData?.actualSearchTerm || adobeopt.queryParam( "keyword" );
        }
        amod.log( "searchDeferred: firing", searchInit );
        pcl.addEvent( 10 );
        pcl.addEvar( 10, searchInit.searchKeyword );
        pcl.addEvar( 11, searchInit.searchType );
        pcl.addEvar( 79, searchInit.searchCat );
        // pcl.addEvar( 95, getObjRef( digitalData, "actualSearchTerm" ) );
      }
    }
  } catch ( ex ) {
    amod.exception( ex );
  }
}

pmc.pageViewTypeHandlers = {

  "Search": function(data) {
    // event10
    // report the 
    pcl.addEvar( 10, window?.digitalData?.actualSearchTerm );

    // evar15 - REVIEW this should come from data layer
    amod.trySafe( "search-sort", function() {
      let sortbyElement = adobeopt.dom.query("#Select_sort_by").firstNode();
      let sortByText = sortbyElement.options[sortbyElement.selectedIndex].text;
      pcl.addEvar( 15, sortByText );
    });

    if ( window.location.search.indexOf("currentPage") == -1 ) { // only on first page of results
        // generate product string from search results
        var prodString = pmc.prodStrFromDataLayerObj( digitalData, "searchPageView" );
        pcl.setProductString( prodString );
    }
    pmc.setFusionMetrics();

  },

  "Product Detail": function(data) {
    pcl.addEvent( 17 ); // product detail page
    var prodString = pmc.prodStrFromDataLayerObj( digitalData.product || {}, "productDetail" );
    pcl.setProductString( prodString );
    // all products are costco next currently
    pcl.addEvar( 18, "Single SKU" );
    pcl.addEvar( 20, "na" );
    pcl.addEvar( 99, "in stock" );
  }

};

function ifQueryStrParam(paramName, /* fnc or */ eventNum, evarNum, attribution, fnc) {
  let paramVal = adobeopt.queryParam(paramName);
  if (typeof paramVal === "string" && paramVal !== '') {
      if (typeof arguments[1] === "function") {
          fnc = arguments[1];
      }
      if (fnc) {
          fnc(paramVal, arguments);
      } else {
          if ( eventNum ) {
            pcl.addEvent(eventNum);
          }
          pcl.addEvar(evarNum, paramVal);
          if (attribution) {
              pcl.addEvar(28, attribution); // last touch attribution
              pcl.addEvar(29, attribution); // first touch attribution
              pmc.findingMethod = attribution;
          }
      }
  }
}

pmc.dlEventHandlers = {
    "pageView": function( data, action ) {
        if ( window.location.pathname == "/SinglePageCheckoutView" ) {
            return;
        }
        pcl.addEvent( 1 );
        ifQueryStrParam("EMID", /* event */ 30, /* evar */ 30, "Email");
        ifQueryStrParam("EXTID", 31, 31, "External link");
        ifQueryStrParam("COSTID", 32, 32, "Costco link");
        ifQueryStrParam("SOCID", 33, 33, "Social link");
        ifQueryStrParam("QRID", 34, 34, "QR Code");
        ifQueryStrParam("ADBUTLERID", 0, 35, "AdButler");
        ifQueryStrParam("NATAPP", 104, 104);
        ifQueryStrParam("NAE", 105, 105, "Native Home Espot");
        ifQueryStrParam("PUSHID", 107, 107, "PushNotification");    
        pmc.pageViewTypeHandlers?.[digitalData.pageType]?.( data );
        pmc.searchFireDeferred(); // deferred search initiations
        pcl.fireDeferred(); // other deferred events
        pcl.fireEvt();
    },
    "search": function( data, action ) { // search initiation

        sessionStorage.setItem( "aopt-searchinitiation", JSON.stringify( {
            fromUrl: window.location.href,
            searchKeyword: dlEventProp( data, "searchTerm", "search", "[not found]"  ),
            searchType: getObjRef( data, "searchType", "typed" ),
//            actualSearchTerm: getObjRef( data, "actualSearchTerm", "[not found]" ),
//            fusionQueryId: getObjRef( data, "fusionQueryId", "[not found]" ),
            searchCat: "All Products"
        }) );

        return;
    },
    "searchClick": function(data, action) {
      pcl.addEvent( 13 ); // searchClick
      let prodString = pmc.prodStrFromDataLayerObj( data, "searchClick" );
      pcl.setProductString( prodString );
      pmc.setFusionMetrics();
      action.analyticsLink = 'dl:searchClick';
    },
    "ui": function( data, action ) {
        if ( data.defer ) {
            pcl.beacon.defer = true;
        }
        pcl.addEvent( 14 );
        pcl.addEvar( 14, dlEventProp( data, "uiName", "ui", true ) );
        action.analyticsLink = 'dl:ui';
        return;
    },
    "nav": function( data, action ) {
        // try {
        //     if ( data.element.tagName === "A" ) {
        //         data.linktext = cleanText( data.element.textContent );
        //     }
        // } catch ( ex ) { };
        // data.navName = adobeopt.tag.resolveValue( data, dlEventProp( data, "navName", "nav", true ) );
        if ( data.defer ) {
            pcl.beacon.defer = true;
        }
//        pmc.navClick ( data.element, data.navName );

        pcl.addEvent( 6 );
        pcl.addEvar( 6, dlEventProp( data, "navName", "nav", true ) );
        action.analyticsLink = 'dl:nav';

        return;
    },
    "espot": function( data, action ) {
        pcl.addEvent( 5 );
        pcl.addEvar( 5, dlEventProp( data, "espotName", "espot", "[not found]"  ) );
        if ( data.defer ) {
            pcl.beacon.defer = true;
        }
        action.analyticsLink = 'eSpot click';
        return;
    },
    "whSearch": function( data, action ) {
        pcl.addEvent( 40 );
        pcl.addEvar( 40, dlEventProp( data, "whSearchTerm", "whSearch", "[not found]"  ) );
        pcl.addEvar( 41, getObjRef( data, "whSearchLoc", "[not found]" ) );
        action.analyticsLink = 'dl:whSearch';
        return;
    },
    "uimsg": function( data, action ) {
        let uimsg = dlEventProp( data, "uimsgText", "uimsg", "[not found]"  );

        // temporarily filter out swatch messages
        let uimsgParts = uimsg.split(" | ");
        if ( uimsgParts.length > 1 && uimsgParts[0] === "Product Detail" )
        {
            if ( uimsgParts[1] !== "Tooltip" && uimsgParts[1] !== "Pick-Up" ) {
                return;
            }
        }

        pcl.addEvent( 37 );
        pcl.addEvar( 37, uimsg );
        if ( pmc.pageLoadFired === true ) {
            action.analyticsLink = 'dl:uimsg';
        }
        return;
    },
    "cartAdd": function( data, action ) {

        let prods = pmc.prodsFromDataLayerObj( data, [], "addToCart" );
        if ( prods.length === 0 ) {
            return;
        }
        pcl.addEvent( 24 );

        var lastReco = localStorage.getItem( "pmc-reco-last-clicked" );
        var lastRecoId = "";
        var lastRecoCriteria = "";
        var lastRecoPageType = "";
        if ( lastReco != undefined ) {
            lastReco = lastReco.split("|");
            if ( lastReco.length > 2 ) {
                lastRecoId = lastReco[0];
                lastRecoCriteria = lastReco[1];
                lastRecoPageType = lastReco[2];
            }
        }
        let cartAddLoc = dlEventProp( data, "cartAdd", "cartAddLoc", "[not found]" );
        prods.forEach( function( prod ) {
            prod.addEvar( 24, cartAddLoc );
            if ( prod.pid === lastRecoId ) {
                pcl.addEvar( 77, lastRecoCriteria );
                pcl.addEvar( 78, lastRecoPageType );
            }
        });

        // event can only fire with atc
        if ( data.pickupAdd !== undefined ) {
            pcl.addEvent( 27 );
        }
        
        pcl.setProductString( pmc.prodStrFromProds( prods ) );
        action.analyticsLink = 'dl:cart add';

    },
    "cartRemove": function( data, action ) {

        let prods = pmc.prodsFromDataLayerObj( data );
        if ( prods.length === 0 ) {
            return;
        }
        pcl.addEvent( 25 );
            
        pcl.setProductString( pmc.prodStrFromProds( prods ) );
        if ( data.defer ) {
            pcl.beacon.defer = true;
        }
        action.analyticsLink = 'dl:cart remove';

    },
    "cancel": function( data, action ) {

        let prods = pmc.prodsFromDataLayerObj( data );
        if ( prods.length === 0 ) {
            return;
        }
        pcl.addEvent( 7 );
        pcl.addEvar( 7, dlEventProp( data, "cancel", "orderCancelLoc", "[not found]" ) );
        pcl.setProductString( pmc.prodStrFromProds( prods ) );
        action.analyticsLink = 'dl:order cancel';

    },
    "filter": function( data, action ) {
        let isCategory = pmc.pageType == "Category";

        pcl.addEvent( isCategory ? 8 : 12 );
        pcl.addEvar( isCategory ? 8 : 12, typeof data.filterVal === "string" ? data.filterVal : "[not found]" );
        pcl.addEvar( isCategory ? 9 : 13, dlEventProp( data, "filter", "filterCat", "[not found]" ) );
        action.analyticsLink = 'dl:filter applied';

    },
    "filterRemove": function( data, action ) {

        pcl.addEvent( 108 );
        pcl.addEvar( 108, typeof data.filterVal === "string" ? data.filterVal : "[not found]" );
        pcl.addEvar( 109, dlEventProp( data, "filterRemove", "filterCat", "[not found]" ) );
        action.analyticsLink = 'dl:filter removed';

    },
    "addListener": function( data, action ) {
        let values = data.addListener;
        adobeopt.tag.addListener( values.on, values.dsel, values.fire );
    },
    "diag": function( data, action ) {

        pcl.addEvent( 66 );
        pcl.addEvar( 66, dlEventProp( data, "diag", "diagMsg", "[not found]" ) );
        action.analyticsLink = 'dl:diag';

    },
    "targetImp": function( data, action ) {
        if ( data.element ) {
            pmc.targetRecoImpression( data.element );
        }        
    },
    "targetClick": function( data, action ) {
        if ( data.element ) {
            pmc.targetRecoClick( data.element );
        }
    },
    "emailSignup": function( data, action ) {
      pcl.addEvent( 44 );
      pcl.addEvar( 44, dlEventProp( data, "emailSignupLoc", "emailSignup", "[not found]" ) );
      action.analyticsLink = 'dl:emailSignup';
    },
    "checkoutEvent": function( data, action ) {
      pcl.addEvent( 56 );
      pcl.addEvar( 56, data.checkoutEvent );
      action.analyticsLink = 'dl:checkoutEvent';
    },
    "videoLinkClick": function( data, action ) {
      pcl.addEvent( 55 );
      action.analyticsLink = 'dl:videoLinkClick';
    },
    "costcoBalance": function( data, action ) {
      pcl.addEvent( 54 );
      pcl.addEvar( 54, dlEventProp( data, "costcoBalance", "costcoBalanceDesc", "[not found]" ) );
      action.analyticsLink = 'dl:costcoBalance';

    },
    "countBalance": function( data, action ) {
      let amt = dlEventProp( data, "countBalance", "dollarBalance", "0.00" );
      try {
          if ( typeof amt == "string" ) {
              amt = parseFloat(amt);
          } else if ( typeof amt !== "number" ) {
            amt = 0;
          }
          amt = amt.toLocaleString("en-US", { maximumFractionDigits: 2, minimumFractionDigits: 2 });
      } catch ( ex ) { }
      pcl.addEvent( 52, amt );
      pcl.addEvent( 53 );
      action.analyticsLink = 'dl:countBalance';
    }
};

/** ENDMODULE datalayer_ecom **/

/** MODULE datalayer **/

let ddeCollectFromAttrib = pmc.ddeCollectFromAttrib = function( attrib, data ) {

    var trAttr = data.trAttr;
    if ( data.element && trAttr ) {
        if ( trAttr.indexOf("data-bi-") != 0 ) {
            trAttr = "data-bi-tr-" + trAttr;
        }
        var $element = null;
        if ( data.event ) {
            $element = dom.query( data.event.target );
        } else if ( data.element ) {
            $element = dom.query( data.element );
        }
        if ( $element === null ) {
            return;
        }
        var tr = $element.attr( trAttr );
        if ( tr == undefined ) { // avoid using selector unless it's not on the element
            tr = $element.closest("[" + trAttr + "]").attr(trAttr);
        }
        if ( tr != undefined ) {
            var trprops = pmc.parseDdeProps( tr );
            for ( var prop in trprops ) {
                if ( !data.hasOwnProperty(prop) ) { // data values override trAttrib values
                    data[prop] = trprops[prop];
                }
            }
        }
    }
}

pmc.processDataLayerEventBlock = function( eventBlock ) {

    pcl.clearSObj();

    let dlmod = adobeopt.module("datalayer");

    // optionally collect values from an attribute of the element 
    if ( eventBlock.hasOwnProperty("trAttr") ) {
        ddeCollectFromAttrib( eventBlock.trAttr, eventBlock );
    }
    // inspect with collected values
    if ( biInspectEnabled && biInspectEvents && !eventBlock.hasOwnProperty("addListener") ) {
        biInspectEvents.push( adobeopt.extend( { _type:"digitalDataEvents:push" }, eventBlock ) );
    }

    var eventName = eventBlock.event;
    if ( eventName !== undefined && pmc.dlEventHandlers[eventName] !== undefined && eventBlock[eventName] == undefined ) {
        eventBlock[eventName] = 1;
    }
    pmc.dataLayerEventBlock = eventBlock;
    let action = {};
    for( eventName in eventBlock ) {
        if ( pmc.dlEventHandlers[eventName] !== undefined ) {
            dlmod.trySafe( "processDataLayerEventBlock:" + eventName, function() {
                pmc.dlEventHandlers[ eventName ]( eventBlock, action );                
            });
        }
    }
    if ( action.analyticsLink !== undefined ) {
      pmc.fireEvt( true, 'o', action.analyticsLink );
    }
    pmc.dataLayerEventBlock = undefined;
};

let dlStrValue = pmc.dlStrValue = function( str, omit1 ) {
    if ( "string|boolean|number".indexOf( typeof str ) > -1 ) {
        str = str.toString();
        if ( omit1 == true && str == "1" ) {
            return undefined;
        }
        if ( str.length > 0 ) {
            return str;
        }
    }
    return undefined;
}

let dlEventProp = pmc.dlEventProp = function( data, propName, evtName, def ) {
    var r = dlStrValue( data[propName] );
    if ( r !== undefined ) {
        return r;
    }
    var r = dlStrValue( data[evtName], true );
    if ( r !== undefined ) {
        return r;
    }
    return def;
}

pmc.parseDdeProps = function( str, element ) {
    var dlo = { };
    if ( element ) {
        dlo.element = element;
    }
    var props = str.split(";");
    props.forEach( function( prop, i ) {
        var args = prop.split(":",2);
        dlo[args[0]] = args.length == 2 ? args[1] : 1;
        if ( args[0] != "pageView" && pmc.dlEventHandlers.hasOwnProperty(args[0]) ) {
            dlo["event"] = args[0];
        }
    });
    return dlo;
}

pmc.pagesByType = { };
pmc.pagesByPath = [ ];
let addPageHandler = pmc.addPageHandler = function( o ) {
	pmc.pagesByPath.push( o );
};
pmc.onPageViewProcs = [ ];
pmc.onPageView = function( name, fnc ) {
	pmc.onPageViewProcs.push( { name:name, fnc:fnc } );
};
pmc.pageTaggingProcs = [ ];
pmc.addPageTagging = function( name, fnc ) {
	pmc.pageTaggingProcs.push( { name:name, fnc:fnc } );
};

pmc.getDebugValue = function( name ) {
  var r = adobeopt.queryParam( name );
  if ( pcl.strNotBlank( r ) )
      return r;
  return pcl.strOrBlank( localStorage.getItem( name ) );
};


pmc.documentReady = function() {

    pmc.fDebug = pmc.fDebugExceptions = pmc.getDebugValue('pointmarcDebug') === "yes"; // localStorage.setItem('pointmarcDebug','yes')

    pcl.initalize();

    var fDisableEvents = false;

    // if ( window.location.pathname === "/SinglePageCheckoutView" ) {
    //     // this page has bugs where the data layer was implemented incorrectly
    //     // so we're disabling for now
    //     fDisableEvents = true;
    // }
    
    var eventBacklog = [ ];
    if ( !fDisableEvents ) {
        if ( Array.isArray( window.digitalDataEvents ) ) {
            // the page was intialized with a data layer page view event so process that
            // assert that if ( typeof window.digitalDataEvents.eventHistory !== "undefined" ) { 
            // if digitalDataEvents undefined or does not include the property "eventHistory" 
            // then datalayer has not been initialized
            eventBacklog = window.digitalDataEvents; // array backlog of events that fired before tag manager loaded
            delete window["digitalDataEvents"];
        }
        if ( window.digitalDataEvents === undefined ) {
            window.digitalDataEvents = {
                eventHistory: [ ],
                push: function( newEvent, element ) {
                    if ( typeof newEvent == "string" ) {
                        newEvent = pmc.parseDdeProps( newEvent, element );
                    }
                    pmc.processDataLayerEventBlock( newEvent ); // call DTM/any tag manager
                }
            }
        }
    }
    // if ( eventBacklog.length === 0 || eventBacklog[0].pageView  === undefined ) {
    //     // if there is an empty eventBacklog or the first event in the backlog is not a pageview
    //     // fire our default page view
    //     if ( pmc.pageViewLegacy ) {
    //       pmc.pageViewLegacy();
    //     }
    //     else {
    //       digitalDataEvents.push( { pageView:1 } );
    //     }
    // } else if ( pmc.debugDataLayerEvents ) {
    //     amod.log( "digitalDataEvent: window.digitalDataEvents contains pageView, skipped default page view" );
    // }
    // post backlog of events
    eventBacklog.forEach( function( evt ) {
        window.digitalDataEvents.push(evt);
    });

    adobeopt.tag.addListener( "click", 'body ~~ [data-bi-tc] a, a[data-bi-tc], button[data-bi-tc], [data-bi-tc] button, input[type="button"][data-bi-tc], [data-bi-tc] input[type="button"], ' +
        'input[type="checkbox"][data-bi-tc], [data-bi-tc] input[type="checkbox"], input[type="submit"][data-bi-tc], [data-bi-tc] input[type="submit"]', 
        { trAttr: "data-bi-tc" }
    );
    adobeopt.tag.addListener( "click", 'body ~~ [data-bi-tca]', { trAttr: "data-bi-tca" } );
    adobeopt.tag.addListener( "change", 'body ~~ [data-bi-tchange]', { trAttr: "data-bi-tchange" } );

    let isInViewport = function (el) {
        try {
            var rect = el.getBoundingClientRect();
            return (
                rect.top >= 0 &&
                rect.left >= 0 &&
                rect.bottom > 0 &&
                rect.right > 0 &&
                rect.bottom <= (window.innerHeight || document.documentElement.clientHeight) &&
                rect.right <= (window.innerWidth || document.documentElement.clientWidth)
            );
        } catch(ex) { amod.log( "isInViewport", ex ) }
        return false;
    }

    if ( adobeopt.isJqueryLoaded() ) {
      $(window).on( 'DOMContentLoaded load resize scroll', adobeopt.debounce( function () {
        amod.log("checking visibility");
        var elements = $("[data-bi-timp]:not([data-bi-timpfired])").each( function() {
            amod.log("checking visibility element");
            if ( isInViewport( this ) ) {
                amod.log("checking visibility element isInViewport");
                $(this).attr("data-bi-timpfired", "true");
                digitalDataEvents.push( { trAttr:"data-bi-timp", element:this } );
            }
        }); 
      }, 1000, false ) );

    }

    function dispatch( handlers ) {
      if ( false ) {
          for( var key in handlers ) {
              // when debugging, allow exceptions to halt execution
              handlers[key].fnc();
          }
      } else {
          for( var key in handlers ) {
              try {
                  handlers[key].fnc();
              } catch ( ex ) {
                  amod.exception( ex, "in " + key );
              }
          }
      }
  }

  dispatch( pmc.onPageViewProcs );

  // fire page view
  // global variable can be sent to supress events from firing
      // this is set when redirecting
  if ( window.pmcSuppressPageLoadEvent === true  ) {
      /** DEBUG PDB( "Suppressing Page Load Event" ); **/
      pcl.clearSObj();
  } else {

    // temporary tagging for search initiation
    // REVIEW this should come from data layer call
    function searchInitiation() {
      digitalDataEvents.push( {
        search: adobeopt.dom.query('[data-testid="SearchBarUI"] input[aria-label="Search"]').firstNode()?.value,
        searchType: "typed"
      });
    }

    adobeopt.dom.query('[data-testid="SearchBarUI"] input[aria-label="Search"]').firstNode()?.addEventListener('keypress', function (e) {
      if (e.key === 'Enter') {
        searchInitiation();
      }
    }, { capture: true, passive: true } );
    adobeopt.dom.query('[data-testid="SearchBarUI"] button[aria-label="Search"]').firstNode()?.addEventListener('click', searchInitiation, { capture: true, passive: true } );

    digitalDataEvents.push( { pageView:1 } );

  }

  // execute pageListener tagging
  dispatch( pmc.pageTaggingProcs );

}

/** ENDMODULE datalayer **/

/** MODULE datalayer_ecom **/

let stripCanonicalPath = pmc.stripCanonicalPath = function( path ) {
  if ( path.indexOf(".product.") > -1 ) {
      // strip canonical portion of path to keep v74 uniform
      var myRegexp = /(\.product\..*\.html)/g;
      var match = myRegexp.exec( path );
      if ( match ) {
          path = "/" + match[1];
      }
  }
  return path;
}

pmc.varsForAllEvents = function() {

  try {

      if ( _satellite.getVar("OneTrust Opt Out?") === true ) {
          amod.diag("opted out, setting s.abort");
          s.abort = true;
          return;
      }

      let buildinfo = "";

      if ( _satellite.getVar("isPageModernized?" ) ) {
        try {
          buildinfo = "modernized L:" + _satellite.buildInfo.buildDate + _satellite.environment.stage.slice(0,3);
        } catch (e) { };
        pcl.addEvar( 1, window?.digitalData?.pageName );
        pcl.addEvar( 2, window?.digitalData?.pageType ); 
        pcl.addEvar( 3, window?.digitalData?.pagePlatform || "Unknown" );
        pcl.addEvar( 4, window?.digitalData?.siteLang ); 
        pcl.addEvar( 7, window?.digitalData?.pageCMS || "Unknown" );

        pcl.addEvar( 26, window?.digitalData?.authStatus || "Unknown" );

        let crumbs = window?.digitalData?.pageCrumbs;
        if ( Array.isArray(crumbs) && crumbs.length > 0 ) {
          pcl.addEvar( 63, crumbs[0] );
          pcl.addEvar( 64, crumbs.join(" | ") );
        }

        pcl.addEvar( 75, buildinfo );
        
      } else {

        pcl.addEvar( 1, pmc.pageName + pmc.pageNameExt );
        pcl.addEvar( 2, pmc.pageType );
        pcl.addEvar( 4, pmc.lang );
        pcl.addEvar( 63, pmc?.V63BreadCrumbs?.trim() );
        pcl.addEvar( 64, pmc?.V64BreadCrumbs?.trim() );
        try {
          buildinfo = document.querySelector("meta[name='currentBuildNumber']")?.getAttribute('content');
          buildinfo += " A:" + pmc.ver;
          buildinfo += " L:" + _satellite.buildInfo.buildDate + _satellite.environment.stage.slice(0,3);
        } catch (e) { };
        if ( _satellite.getVar("useAlloy") ) {
          buildinfo += " websdk";
        }
        pcl.addEvar( 75, buildinfo );

      }

      let kmsiCookie = _satellite.cookie.get('kmsi');
      let kmsi = ! ( typeof kmsiCookie == 'undefined' || kmsiCookie == null || kmsiCookie  == 'false');
      pcl.addEvar( 36, kmsi ? "true" : "false" );

      let appPlatform = localStorage.getItem( "aopt-appPlatform" );
      if ( typeof appPlatform == "string" ) {
          pcl.addEvar( 46, appPlatform );
      }
      
      if ( digitalDataEx.memberLoggedIn == "yes" && digitalDataEx.siteStoreCountry == "bcus" ) {
        let costcoHashId = _satellite.cookie.get("costcoHashId");
        if ( typeof costcoHashId === "string" ) {
            pcl.addEvar( 21, costcoHashId )
        }    
      }

      layoutMode = "desktop"; // desktop | tablet | mobile

      try {
        let getScreenType = adobeopt.deepRef( window, "COSTCO.util.getScreenType" );
        if ( getScreenType ) {
            var lm = getScreenType();
    
            if ( lm.indexOf ("PHONE") > -1 ) {
                layoutMode = "mobile";
            } else if ( lm.indexOf ("TABLET") > -1 ) {
                layoutMode = "tablet";
            } // else DESKTOP
        }
      } catch ( e ) { 
        pmc.diagnostic.push("vfav:gst") 
      }

      pcl.addEvar( 70, layoutMode ); // eVar70
      pcl.addEvar( 71, window.location.host );
      // pcl.addEvar( 73, pmc.GetPSTDateString() );

      pcl.addEvar( 74, stripCanonicalPath(window.location.pathname) );

      try {
          pmc.automatedTestId = adobeopt.queryParam("qaTestID");
          if ( pmc.automatedTestId !== undefined ) {
              localStorage.setItem("automatedTestId", pmc.automatedTestId );
          } else {
              pmc.automatedTestId = localStorage.getItem("automatedTestId");
          }
          if ( pcl.strNotBlank( pmc.automatedTestId ) ) {
              pcl.addEvar( 100, pmc.automatedTestId );
          }
      } catch (ex) {  }

      if ( pmc.isBusDel ) {
          var WC_BD_WHS = _satellite.cookie.get("WC_BD_WHS");
          if ( typeof WC_BD_WHS == "string" && WC_BD_WHS.length > 0 ) {
              pcl.addEvar( 84, WC_BD_WHS );
          }
          var WC_BD_ZIP = _satellite.cookie.get("WC_BD_ZIP");
          if ( typeof WC_BD_ZIP == "string" && WC_BD_ZIP.length > 0 ) {
              pcl.addEvar( 49, WC_BD_ZIP );
          }
      } else {
          try {
              var whdata = JSON.parse( _satellite.cookie.get('WAREHOUSEDELIVERY_WHS') );
              pcl.addEvar( 84, whdata.groceryCenters[0] );
          } catch(e) { }
          try {
              var storedata = JSON.parse( _satellite.cookie.get('STORELOCATION') );
              pcl.addEvar( 86, storedata.storeLocation.city );
          } catch(e) { }
          try {
              var zipcode = _satellite.cookie.get('invCheckPostalCode');
              pcl.addEvar( 49, zipcode != undefined ? zipcode : "" );
          } catch(e) { }
      }

      let urlParams = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
      let urlParamsFiltered = [];
      urlParams.forEach(function (value, key) {
          if ( key !== "krypto") {
              urlParamsFiltered.push(key + '=' + encodeURIComponent(value));
          }
      });
      var pageurl = window.location.href.split("?")[0]; // review: hash
      if (urlParamsFiltered.length > 0) {
          pageurl +=  '?' + urlParamsFiltered.join("&");
      }
      // REVIEW is pageUrl used?
      // ADO #349755
      pcl.addEvar( 69, adobeopt.cleanUrl( window.location ) );

  } catch( e ) {
    amod.exception(e);
    pmc.diagnostic.push("vfav");
  }

};

// fire event
pmc.fireEvt = function( a1, a2, a3 ) {
  pmc.varsForAllEvents();
  if ( pmc.diagnostic.length > 0 ) {
      pcl.addEvent( 66 );
      pcl.addEvar( 66, pmc.diagnostic.join("|").slice( 0, 200 ) );
      pmc.diagnostic = [ ];
  }
  pmc.fixUpReferrer( false );
  
  if ( pmc.inPrivateElement ) {
      amod.log( "inPrivateElement: suppressing event" );
      pcl.beacon.suppressedPrivate = true;
      pcl.clearSObj();
  } else {
      pcl.submitToAnalytics( a1, a2, a3 );
  }

  pmc.trackParams = { };
  pmc.diagnostic = [ ];
};

pmc.fixUpReferrer = amod.tryWrap( "fixUpReferrer", function( isPageView ) {
  digitalDataEx.sessionAnalyticsBeaconCt = adobeopt.sessionIncCounter("biBeaconCt");
  if ( isPageView ) {
      digitalDataEx.sessionAnalyticsPageViewCt = adobeopt.sessionIncCounter("biPageViewCt");
  }
  let referrer = document.referrer;
  if ( typeof referrer === "string" && referrer.length > 0 ) {
      if ( referrer.indexOf("signin.costco.com") > -1 ) {
          pcl.beacon.referrer = window.location.origin + "/signin_costco_com";
          return "fixing signin";
      }
  }
  if ( isPageView && digitalDataEx.sessionAnalyticsPageViewCt === 1 ) {
      let savedReferrer = adobeopt.deepRef( digitalDataEx, "sessionLandingPage.referrer" );
      if ( savedReferrer !== referrer ) {
          amod.diag("fixUpReferrer:using session referrer",savedReferrer);
          pcl.beacon.referrer = savedReferrer;
          return "using sessionLandingPage.referrer";
      }
  }
  return "no change";
});

/** ENDMODULE datalayer_ecom **/

});
 </script>
 <script>
  _satellite["_runScript2"](function(event, target, Promise) {
window.adobe = window.adobe || {};
window.adobe.target = window.adobe.target || {};
window.adobe.target.getOffer = function( options ) {
    let pageParamsAll = window.targetPageParamsAll ? window.targetPageParamsAll() : {};
    let sendEventParams = {
        renderDecisions: false,
         personalization: {
           sendDisplayEvent: false
        },
        decisionScopes: [ options.mbox ],
        type: "decisioning.propositionFetch",
        data: {
            "__adobe": {
                "target": {
                    ...pageParamsAll,
                    ...options.params
                }
            }
        }
    };
    adobeopt.alloy("sendEvent", sendEventParams).then( response=>{
        if ( response?.decisions?.[0]?.items?.[0]?.schema == "https://ns.adobe.com/personalization/json-content-item" ) {
            response = [{
                "action": "setJson",
                "content": [
                  response?.decisions?.[0]?.items?.[0]?.data?.content
                ]
            }];
        }
        if ( response?.decisions?.[0]?.items?.[0]?.schema == "https://ns.adobe.com/personalization/html-content-item" ) {
            response = [{
                "action": "setContent",
                "content": response?.decisions?.[0]?.items?.[0]?.data?.content
            }];
        }
        options.success( response );
    }).catch( error=>{
        options.error( error );
    });
}
window.adobe.target.getOffers = function (options) {
  let pageParamsAll = window.targetPageParamsAll
    ? window.targetPageParamsAll()
    : {};
  let scope = [];
  let mboxParams = {};
  options?.request?.execute?.mboxes.forEach((mbox) => {
    const { name, parameters } = mbox;
    scope.push(name);
  });
  let sendEventParams = {
    renderDecisions: false,
    personalization: {
      sendDisplayEvent: false
    },
    type: "decisioning.propositionFetch",
    decisionScopes: [...scope],
    data: {
      __adobe: {
        target: {
          ...pageParamsAll
        },
      },
    },
  };
  adobeopt.alloy('sendEvent', sendEventParams).then((response) => {
    let meta = {};
    if (
      Array.isArray(response?.propositions) &&
      response?.propositions.length > 0
    ) {
      let eventPropositions = response.propositions.filter((proposition) =>
        scope.includes(proposition.scope)
      );
      eventPropositions.forEach((proposition) => {
        let selector = '';
        if (!proposition.scope.includes('data')) {
          try {
            selector = '[data-mboxph-name="' + proposition.scope + '"]';
            let mbxele = document.querySelector(selector);
            if (mbxele != null) {
              mbxele.dataset.mboxphStatus = 'applied';
              proposition.items[0].data.selector = selector;
              proposition.items[0].data.type = 'insertAfter';
              const jsonMbox = {
                name: proposition.scope,
                options: [{ content: proposition.items[0].data.content }],
              };
              if (adobeopt.dom.handleJsonOffer(jsonMbox, mbxele, selector)) {
                mbxele.dataset.mboxphStatusDet = 'jsonOffer';
                return;
              }
            }            
          }
          catch( ex ) { _satellite.logger.error( "mbox ph apply exception", ex ) }
        } else {
          selector = 'HEAD';
        }
        meta[proposition.scope] = {
          selector: selector,
          actionType: 'appendHtml',
        };
      });
      alloy('applyPropositions', {
        propositions: eventPropositions,
        metadata: meta,
      }).then((response) => {
        return response;
      });
    } else {
      return response;
    }
  });
};
});
